additional_data.description: The spirit of a glottonous monster from Greek mythology. He likes to travel far and wide in search of delicious food, though of late he never seems to leave Japan. Since eventually all the world's delicacies end up there, he's decided to just wait for them to come to him. Despite his reputation as a gourmet, he isn't that picky about things like flavor profiles or ingredient quality. He just cares about if he likes the food.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" Event: Clear Chapter 4.
◦ "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" Event: Exchange for 1000 Wish Tablet
◦ "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" Event: Get a First Half Ranking of 2501-6000.
◦ "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" Event: Get a Total Ranking of 5001-7500.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slightly increases the drop rate of Wish Tablet during the "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" event.
